        "TileImage": "$($repository 3e3e3752-37db-4b0f-8ff3-827d4c565e55).Image",
        "Description": "Good Evening Agent,\r\rSebastian Sato slipped away from Paris and is now laying low in Dubai, hoping the heat will keep attention off him. \r\rA helicopter is being prepped for a quick exit at any moment, while a few loyal hands keep watch and make sure nothing interrupts his stay. \r\rUnfortunately for Sato, things in Dubai tend to get… very hot. Accidents happen. Flames spread. And escape plans don’t always go as expected.\r\rGood Luck 47.\rBy reTwiice",
